sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser
    participant API as API Routes
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Browser: Select farm from profile editing tabs

    alt Add Resource
        User->>Browser: "Add Crop" / "Add Livestock" / etc.
        Browser->>API: POST /api/{resource-type}
        Note right of Browser: { farmId, type, quantity, ... }
        API->>DB: Resource.create(data)
        DB-->>API: New resource
    else Update Resource
        User->>Browser: Edit resource details
        Browser->>API: PATCH /api/{resource-type}?id={id}
        API->>DB: Resource.update(data)
        DB-->>API: Updated resource
    else Delete Resource
        User->>Browser: Remove resource
        Browser->>API: DELETE /api/{resource-type}?id={id}
        API->>DB: Resource.delete(id)
        DB-->>API: Deleted
    end
    API-->>Browser: Success response
    Browser-->>User: Updated resource list
